        <item>
          <title>TikTok Faces Shutdown in US Amid Supreme Court Ruling</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TikTok's Chinese parent company is required to sell its US operations by January 19, or the app will be shut down. The Biden administration has failed to provide necessary clarity for service providers, leaving TikTok to go dark in the US.]]></description>
